<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-7512] Cannot call Trait method from Closure when using static compilation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-7512</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When running:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeHeader panelHeader&quot; style=&quot;border-bottom-width: 1px;border-bottom-style: solid;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;test.groovy&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;X {
    Closure action = {}
}

trait T {

    void say(&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; text) {
        println text
    }

    @groovy.transform.CompileStatic
    X getX() {
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; X(action: {
            say &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;Hello!&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
        })
    }

}

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;A &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;implements&lt;/span&gt; T {
}

&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; A().x.action()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The following exception is thrown:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;Caught: java.lang.ClassCastException: java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Class&lt;/span&gt; cannot be &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;cast&lt;/span&gt; to T
java.lang.ClassCastException: java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Class&lt;/span&gt; cannot be &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;cast&lt;/span&gt; to T
	at T$Trait$Helper$_getX_closure1.doCall(test.groovy:14)
	at T$Trait$Helper$_getX_closure1.doCall(test.groovy)
	at test.run(test.groovy:23)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is only happening on groovy 2.4.4. Removing the static compilation annotation or reverting to groovy version 2.4.3 makes the code work. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The commit that is causing this problem seems to be: 1bbed25aa3a08bc0cb7e14e49a1e7c2b82f21a26&lt;/p&gt;</description>
